title: DDFP 396: Week 6 review & Playoff Picture preview
itunes:title: DDFP 396: Week 6 review & Playoff Picture preview
description:
Shek is joined by Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling to discuss Monday Night Football, as well as the AFC and NFC playoff picture. Then, Handsome Hank, Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew join the show to recap the Panthers vs. Seahawks and react to A.J. Hawk's MJD apology.
